{"tid":1442781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去深水埗既同我入一入嚟！重要！","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:16:16.000Z","uid":268737,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba350b30401595a2f892f7bcf890d698d87f17e1","tid":1442781,"uid":268737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"工作關係，經常出入深水埗，不時同下啲街坊傾計，所以有少少野想提醒下各位<br />\n<br />\n深水埗街坊區，深藍係有，但都有唔少口講中立，但心入面係支持我地既街坊。<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會大大聲講支持，係因為經歷過文革同六四，好驚完左會比黨清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好依個時候就鬧佢地犬儒住，人地真係親身經歷過，我地唔會知佢地既經歷係有幾恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地係大陸落嚟，點會唔知共產黨有幾仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但同時唔好忘記，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢地日常都係師奶仔一個，日日都睇住TVB，日撚日吸收緊林鄭條仆街既記招</span></span>，林鄭依家日日打民生經濟牌，target緊咪依班人[/size=4]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><del>同時冇得唔承認，我地依家真係攪到街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>依班師奶仔其實內心都好掙扎，見到差佬好過份咁打我地會好心痛，但睇完記招又會諗示威者係咪都應該收手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝你會睇個P牌仔廢up到依到，我唔係想割，核爆都唔割呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n只係提提大家，今日遇到啲操鄉音又有少少微言既街坊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好屌佢地住</span></span>，只要我地禮貌啲，有時間就解釋多兩句，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">提多啲元朗黑夜</span></span>，佢地又會傾返去我地依邊架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一句：<br />\nBe water. Be humble. <br />\n終有一天我們可以脫下口罩相見。"},{"pid":"071af37eb38d56371aaa58e3d4f693557d83240c","tid":1442781,"uid":268737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:03:05.000Z","msg":"自推十次，核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dc8a54ccfa4743705701df2525c962f7b613f7","tid":1442781,"uid":268737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"自推十次，核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4babad7f0d0bccff2b8882a2eaa56e6745b2de59","tid":1442781,"uid":268737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"自推十次，核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75af4a7e64b58f38c02a5a5ccadbfa11440274e","tid":1442781,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:07:33.000Z","msg":"推，一陣ssp見"},{"pid":"be18ef0c3240626481ebd76c35c6ff057b101499","tid":1442781,"uid":8753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"深水埗啲呀叔成日都屌警察同政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d765c1948faff6167d727648bc6ca09872c14f4","tid":1442781,"uid":196114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"請禮貌隊隊員多解釋！"},{"pid":"b57909dbeeed1800e34563c387534c586815b801","tid":1442781,"uid":268737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be18ef0c3240626481ebd76c35c6ff057b101499","tid":1442781,"uid":8753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"深水埗啲呀叔成日都屌警察同政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:15:37.000Z","msg":"深水埗啲阿叔好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都好多師奶仔都乜出聲又會食下花生"},{"pid":"a2183c07f57ae82792ad92d13b747a5b8647975e","tid":1442781,"uid":62164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89c2b7739b446117b7161b0ea161d4084dcfdd77","tid":1442781,"uid":268737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57909dbeeed1800e34563c387534c586815b801","tid":1442781,"uid":268737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be18ef0c3240626481ebd76c35c6ff057b101499","tid":1442781,"uid":8753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"深水埗啲呀叔成日都屌警察同政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:15:37.000Z","msg":"深水埗啲阿叔好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都好多師奶仔都乜出聲又會食下花生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"冇乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}